{"tid":1873509,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【良心抗疫】王維基斥156萬出口罩","createTime":"2020-02-10T16:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T02:05:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"474609f6bd53fa13013fc4cc35014bfe9b11fa2a","tid":1873509,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:54:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200210/LJW5OH7YOVA25LL4A3LOFL6AFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2FLJW5OH7YOVA25LL4A3LOFL6AFI%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4Z4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=578df27f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2FLJW5OH7YOVA25LL4A3LOFL6AFI%2F&h=be6a720d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200210/LJW5OH7YOVA25LL4A3LOFL6AFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n【良心抗疫】王維基斥156萬出口罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200210/large/1581253834_8565.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581253834_8565.jpg&h=85467a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王維基生產口罩<br />\n<br />\n疫情下，市面出現瘋搶潮，特區政府無能力補給，市民惟有諗計自救，HKTV的王維基更斥資20萬美元（約156萬港元）購買口罩生產機，希望可暫緩口罩短缺問題。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：教整口罩套功效成疑<br />\n<br />\n王維基生產口罩<br />\n<br />\n旗下HKTVmall在疫情爆發時已派員搜購口罩，日前更親自飛到台灣尋找口罩機器製造商，最終成功以156萬港元購入口罩製造機及相關物料，計劃生產自家口罩，物料足以生產100萬個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：超級後母關心家人<br />\n<br />\n蕭定一製搓手液<br />\n<br />\n自掏腰包設置搓手液生產線工場，免費派發給長者及有需要人士，他表示是由父親蕭若元構思出來。日前他在社交網更上載短片，有工作人員在調製酒精搓手液，並已入樽再裝箱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200210/large/1581253832_8b24.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581253832_8b24.gif&h=86ffe857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n森美撳𨋢神器<br />\n<br />\n在社交網上分享朋友自製的「撳𨋢神器」，把用完的原子筆取出筆芯，當撳電梯時拔開筆蓋，撳完插回，避免用手接觸升降機按鈕，減低沾到病菌的機會，也可以減少使用消毒搓手液。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200210/large/1581253833_ff54.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581253833_ff54.gif&h=1c2b0a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳樂榣製消毒水<br />\n<br />\n前組合Freeze成員陳樂榣，近年轉型從商開設飾品店，日前透露早前添置一部電解氧化水機，其中功能是可製造有殺菌作用的消毒水，市民可自備容器到其公司免費索取，一齊抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200210/large/1581253834_25dc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581253834_25dc.gif&h=c1d6301c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1af414966972f05b1dadbf9bbeac2f565a1c20a","tid":1873509,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"211f3e2e895ed83a56d54f05e8cd98adc57da85b","tid":1873509,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f35e9c770eb0b0ad2db6c5095c3761850e513fa","tid":1873509,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:05:50.000Z","msg":"拉"}]}